    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v1
    tmp = wp.sin(0.22)
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.cos(tmp + 0.06) + (v2 + 0.97 * v0 + 0.55)))
    tmp = ((v2 * wp.cos(v1 + 0.46)) / wp.cos(0.05))
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.cos(tmp + 0.21) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.06)))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.24) - (tmp + 0.49 - tmp + 0.66)) + ((v1 + 0.35 + v1 + 0.07) * (v0 + 0.69 - v0 + 0.65)))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
